    - name: '8-9: '
      title: 
      number: 8-9
      content: "The tribes each selected three men, and as they set out on their
        journey, Joshua told them, \u201CGo through all the land and write down its
        description. When you bring the description back here to me, I will ask <smallcaps>Yahweh</smallcaps>
        in Shiloh to divide the land among your tribes.\u201D So the men went through
        all the land and divided it into seven sections. They wrote a description
        of each section and also made a list of the towns within each section and
        returned to Joshua at Shiloh. "
      comments: []
    - name: '8-9: '
      title: 
      number: 8-9
      content: "The tribes each selected three men, and as they set out on their
