    - name: '25-28: '
      title: 
      number: 25-28
      content: There were another fourteen cities, along with the towns around them,
        which also belonged to the tribe of Benjamin. These cities wereGibeon, Ramah,
        Beeroth,Mizpah, Chephirah, Mozah,Rekem, Irpeel, Taralah,Zela, Haeleph, Jebus
        (or Jerusalem), [[COMMENT(0)]] Gibeah, and Kiriath. Joshua assigned this
        land and all these cities to the tribes of Benjamin.
      comments:
      - number: "18:25\u201328"
        content: '  It is interesting that Jerusalem was not given to the tribe of
          Judah but to the tribe of Benjamin.  '
