    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: "So the people of Israel obeyed <smallcaps>Yahweh</smallcaps>\u2019s
        command and gave the Levites some of their cities and pasturelands from their
        inheritance."
      comments: []
    - name: '4-5: '
      title: 
      number: 4-5
      content: "Each clan of the Levites received its cities by drawing lots. First,
        the people of Israel gave to the descendants of Aaron the priest from the
        clan of Kohath [[COMMENT(0)]] thirteen cities from the territories of Judah,
        Simeon, and Benjamin. They allotted to the rest of the clan of Kohath\u2019s
        descendants ten towns from the clans of the tribes of Ephraim, Dan, and half
        of Manasseh."
      comments:
      - number: "21:4\u20135"
        content: '  The first lot fell to the descendants of Aaron. They were classified
          as priests (see v.  ), while the other descendants of Levi were not.    '
